<Class name="CM_InvoiceLine" id="d30bb59f-68f5-49be-a246-bdd1a697c803">
    <superclass name="CM_FinancialObject"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>One per separate charge for activity in the port.  For cargo things like receive, move, storage and release.  Also to-do tasks, wash, inspect etc.
For voyages things like berthage, costs of other services.
Invoice lines are identified by invoice line type, CM_InvoiceLineDesc.

NOTE: 	If myTransactionVTMIS is populated then this is an invoice line for VOYAGE
		If myTransactionTI is populated then this is an invoice line for TRACKED ITEM
		If myTransactionEvent is populated then this is an invoice line for an EVENT</text>
    <DbClassMap file="invoice"/>
