Used in PEL1 estimates to set the payment type.

This is only used for cash payments for PEL1 estimates.

The cash  uses the invoice module and then aborts the transaction, this means that transactions are lost; 
transactions that are used in the rules for getting the payment type later on in the process.
</text>
